<TEXT>
SANDOZ, like its two Basle-based pharmaceutical competitors Ciba and Roche,
enjoyed strong sales in the third quarter.
Group sales were up 9.7 per cent to SFr3.48bn (Dollars 2.44bn) in the
quarter, led by by a 13.1 per cent jump in pharmaceutical division sales to
