<HEADLINE>
FT  18 OCT 93 / Phones survey
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
ABOUT HALF of all telephone users would change their telephone company if
they were offered free local calls, according to a Gallup survey carried out
for the big cable television companies.
</TEXT>
<XX>
