<TEXT>
THE nomination yesterday of Mr Yusuf Raza Gillani as speaker of the lower
house of the Pakistani parliament, the national assembly, has strengthened
Ms Benazir Bhutto's attempt to become prime minister again.
Her nominee won with a comfortable majority over his rival, Mr Gohar Ayub.
