confident of carrying most of the parties with us,' said Mr Farooq Leghari,
secretary general of the PPP, after yesterday's results. The PPP is expected
to gain the support of independents affiliated to neither of the two
parties.
However, the two sides are still locked in battle for control of Punjab, the
biggest and wealthiest province.
